  <refnamediv>
    <refname>tri2d</refname><refpurpose>Initialise a 3d unstructured triangular surfcae mesh</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>



<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Calling Sequence</title>
   <synopsis>
   th=tri3d()
   mh=tri2d(name)
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
   <varlistentry><term>name :</term>
      <listitem><para> a string, the tri3d's identity</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
     tri3d create a empty typed list containing :
   </para>
   <para>
     Id   : a string identity (empty string by default)
   </para>
   <para>
     Coor : a npx3 mesh point's coordinates matrix
   </para>
   <para>
     Tri  : a ntx3 points index matrix
   </para>
     TriId: a ntx1 domaine indicator matrix
   <para>
     BndId: string vector of the border's name
   </para>
   <para>
     Bnd  : list of the border points by boundary
   </para>
</refsection>

